Package org.jfree.chart.plot

Class XYPlotWrapper

java.lang.Object
org.jfree.chart.block.AbstractContentBlock
org.jfree.chart.plot.XYPlotWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Block, ContentBlock, org.jfree.ui.Drawable
public class XYPlotWrapper extends AbstractContentBlock implements Block
This wrapper presents an XYPlot as a Block that only draws the plot and not the axes.
